{% extends 'layouts/default.layout.njk' %}

{% set pageTitle = 'Collaboration across departments, government and beyond - Learning Platform for Government' %}
{% set blackBarTitle = 'Learning Platform for Government' %} {% set learnerPrototypeVersion = 'v12' %}
{% set mainContainerClass = 'has-lower-hero' %}
{% set signOutPath = '/prototypes/learner/v12/' %}
{% set homePath = '/prototypes/learner/v12/home' %}

{% set resourceType = resourceType if resourceType %}
{% set hideDetailStars = hideDetailStars if hideDetailStars %}


{% block content %}

    {{ components.pageHeading(heading='Collaboration across departments, government and beyond') }}

    {% call components.gridRow() %}

    {% call components.columnTwoThirds() %}

        <p>Increasingly, working collaboratively is a regular part of any civil servant’s life, regardless of profession or grade. The collaboration may be with other government departments or with private and not-for-profit organisations. Either way, it’s important to feel confident in your ability to work effectively with these partners.</p>

          <p>  This topic introduces you to the essential skills and behaviours that underpin successful collaboration, such as:</p>

        <ul class="list-bullet u-space-b30">
            <li>building and maintaining relationships</li>
            <li>sharing control</li>
            <li>recognising and responding to situations of conflict</li>
        </ul>

           <p> You’ll learn about the value of collaboration, how to articulate a shared vision for collaboration and how to maximise the benefits it brings. By being mindful of your partners’ interests and ambitions, you can help ensure that collaboration objectives are met.</p>

    {% call components.formElement(name='startLearning', method='POST', action="#") %}

        {% call components.formGroup() %}
            {{ components.button(text='Start this learning', start=false, group=true)}}
        {%- endcall %}

        <p>
            <a href="/prototypes/learner/v12/actions?action=addedToLearningPlan&type=blog">Add to your learning</a>
        </p>

    {%- endcall %}

    {%- endcall %}

    {% call components.columnOneThird() %}

        <aside class="govuk-related-items govuk-related-items--flush govuk-related-items--keylined" role="complementary">
            <h2 class="heading-small">Key information</h2>

            <table class="table-simple table--top u-space-b30">
                <caption class="visuallyhidden">Details about the course</caption>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Course type</th>
                        <td>Online</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Level</th>
                        <td>AA to Grade 6</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Key area</th>
                        <td>Management</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Duration</th>
                        <td>1 hour</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Cost</th>
                        <td>£Free</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            {% if not hideDetailStars %}
                <h2 class="heading-small">User rating</h2>
                {{ components.starRating(rating='68%', total='97') }}
            {% endif %}

        </aside>

    {%- endcall %}

    {%- endcall %}

{% endblock %}
